==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fiftieth
<hw>Fif"ti*eth</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>f⟦imac⟧ftigo⟦edh⟧a</ets>. See <er>Fifty</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Next in order after the forty-ninth; -- the ordinal of
fifty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Consisting of one of fifty equal parts or
divisions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fiftieth</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Fiftieth
<hw>Fif"ti*eth</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of fifty equal parts; the
quotient of a unit divided by fifty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fifty</ent>⟦br⟧
